reviewText: this is a really cute show that gets kids to use their imaginations and have fun singing silly songs. theres a lot of colors and fun characters to keep kids entertained.
I really enjoyed the wubbulous world of Dr. Seuss: The Cat's Play Pals as well as my daughter. This was very entertaining.

We have gotten our daughter every one of the Wubbulous World of Dr. Seuss movies.  They are creative, short shows with good morals and fun music.  Each movie is a bit different, but they all have funny characters from the various Seuss books, and each character has its own personality.  I can't recommend them enough for children ages 4-9 (my daughter is 9 and she is not ready to part with them yet).

My daughter loves ALL of the Wubbulous World of Dr. Seuss videos.  She could watch the same one over and over; however, I bought the entire collection for a change. Cute, enjoyable and have purchased the entire collection.
